{"tid":147233,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日我生日，個腦諗起一個人","createTime":"2017-03-07T16:57:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T09:25:16.000Z","uid":62495,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7fa267287acd7ad461eecd720a1febb6c1243ed3","tid":147233,"uid":62495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T16:57:13.000Z","msg":"首先好多謝屋企人對我既愛<br />\n養育小弟咁多年 生日最好既禮物係你地健康。<br />\n<br />\n一過12點 好平靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n查緊Email既同時，手痕開番以前Email，發現好多以前既回憶。<br />\n<br />\n有Msn對話 有不知名既留言 有一張張儲存係N世紀的相片。<br />\n<br />\n我諗起你。你陪伴左我三年。<br />\n<br />\n某一日 你同我講我唔成熟，無諗過將來。你仲細 想見識多D，然後一齊係公園喊左一個鐘而分手。<br />\n<br />\n一開始我只係覺得你唔要我，原來係我無好好珍惜你 無為你著想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n某一日 我依舊希望你番番我身邊 見你傷心，我亦主動保護你。<br />\n<br />\n某一日 你同我講希望復合，我無答應。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但我依舊留意你。<br />\n<br />\n某一日 我地不再搵對方，大家的FB 手機 都已經轉曬封面，對話亦封儲了。<br />\n<br />\n直到多年的今日，我地都各自有自己的生活，自己的戀情。<br />\n<br />\n我無後悔同你分開，或者係對你好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我知道你依家同男友同居 佢對你好好 我已經覺得好足夠。我亦有自己的戀情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝你陪伴左我三年 經歷過無數白痴 低能的事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日生日，我諗起既第一人 就係你。<br />\n<br />\n希望 你可以幸福快樂 <br />\n<br />\n希望某一日 你突然諗起我 我地回憶唔係只有傷心 而係會會心微笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n謝謝你愛過我"},{"pid":"e62e2f4c566264298772570ac47811276efabb82","tid":147233,"uid":38934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T16:58:59.000Z","msg":"關我撚事"},{"pid":"bb10fdb9c9b47f4ea086a7b235db3d0ebb096026","tid":147233,"uid":62495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T17:00:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>關我撚事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0866cd92ade71862311ebfcf100117d52b8542a9","tid":147233,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T17:22:47.000Z","msg":"生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a7a7ab84a892a5f0b13176867780269bb70e52b","tid":147233,"uid":33583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T17:25:33.000Z","msg":"我都係今日生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc5e65cfd42335aec720acc56987987674c9b5c0","tid":147233,"uid":62495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T17:25:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  LIHKG有愛"},{"pid":"9b67a514e12d4499275e6064d311a64bace41544","tid":147233,"uid":62495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T17:25:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係今日生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n生日快樂 巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a633c85d16361415eb717a88b370c758da7ca76","tid":147233,"uid":83531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T17:26:42.000Z","msg":"生日快樂 諗起我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99c00b19b6a22a8b9ec2f3943282d40b5070e887","tid":147233,"uid":43116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T17:27:25.000Z","msg":"生日快樂<br />\n祝福你新一年搵到個讓你明白愛的真締嘅人"},{"pid":"0b6cc7c6c1d640e2f9236144c608bd6c60e7b416","tid":147233,"uid":62495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T17:31:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生日快樂 諗起我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝你 呢一刻諗起你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ace0c9708b926cb84d36e1b349e51e160d5b8616","tid":147233,"uid":62495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T17:32:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生日快樂<br />\n祝福你新一年搵到個讓你明白愛的真締嘅人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  人生仲好多路 唔同階段 諗既野都唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n有愛有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76ecd14ccb65d671e973ed927b9a90678b91e0e9","tid":147233,"uid":62495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T09:25:16.000Z","msg":"其實唔知有無機會俾佢睇到 <br />\n如果睇到既 希望你去完旅行就工作順利<br />\n聽朋友講 你番工好辛苦 <br />\n岩岩出黎做野係咁 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}